        "description": "This code worked as expected in R3.4 and arrow package v0.17:\r\n{quote}df <- data.frame(a=bit64::as.integer64(1:10))\r\narrow::write_feather(x=df, sink=\"/home/ofek/tmp/test64\")\r\ndf_read <- arrow::read_feather(\"/home/ofek/tmp/test64\")\r\nclass(df_read$a)   # integer64\r\n{quote}\r\n\r\nBut upgrading to R4+v3.0.0 we see that the output of class(df_read$a) is \"integer\". Stuff breaks as a result.",
