                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Etc/UTC"
                    },
                    "body": "Are you experiencing this only on columns that contain integers that are representable in 32 bits or is it happening even when the column has integers that require 64 bits to be represented?\r\n\r\nAs of Arrow 2.0.0 we have {{options(arrow.int64_downcast = FALSE)}} which should turn off automatic downcasting, have you tried setting that before calling {{arrow::read_feather}}?",
